item.title: The "Two Levels" of Achievement that Can Cure Perfectionism [Episode 166]
item.description: How can we actually feel CONTENT with our progress--instead of feeling behind or inadequate or mixed up with all those feelings of being "imperfect"? Today I'm sharing a powerful thought from a favorite book! See the written version and related links... Feed: https://learndobecome.libsyn.com/rss

item.title: Episode 212: Unforeseen
item.description:
Some of the darkest moments in history happened in the sweet spot between folklore and science. And if one particular event from Philadelphia has anything to teach us, it’s that moments like that are difficult to accept—and more than a little frightening.
